#: ../../source/examples/Example_05_类网格交易.md:1
msgid "类网格交易策略"
msgstr "Psuedo-Grid Trading Strategy"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_05_类网格交易.md:3
msgid ""
"参考来源：`docs/_joinquant_migration_source/Example_05_类网格交"
"易.ipynb` 第一个 Markdown cell。"
msgstr ""
"Reference source: `docs/_joinquant_migration_source/Example_05_Class "
"Grid Trading.ipynb` First Markdown cell."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_05_类网格交易.md:5
msgid "本策略首先计算过去300个价格数据的均值和标准差 (天数是一个可调参数)"
msgstr ""
"This strategy first calculates the mean and standard deviation of the "
"past 300 price data points (the number of days is an adjustable "
"parameter)."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_05_类网格交易.md:6
msgid ""
"并根据均值加减1和2个标准差得到网格的区间分界线,（加减标准差的倍数是可调"
"参数)"
msgstr ""
"The grid interval boundaries are obtained by adding or subtracting 1 "
"and 2 standard deviations from the mean (the multiplier for adding or "
"subtracting standard deviations is an adjustable parameter)."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_05_类网格交易.md:7
msgid "并分别配以0.3和0.5的仓位权重 (仓位权重是可调参数）"
msgstr ""
"They are assigned position weights of 0.3 and 0.5 respectively "
"(position weights are adjustable parameters)."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_05_类网格交易.md:8
msgid ""
"然后根据价格所在的区间来配置仓位(+/-40为上下界,无实际意义): (-40,-3],"
"(-3,-2],(-2,2],(2,3],(3,40](具体价格等于均值+数字倍标准差) [-0.5, -0.3, "
"0.0, 0.3, 0.5] (资金比例,此处负号表示开空仓，回测时设置为允许持有空头仓"
"位)"
msgstr ""
"Then, configure the position size based on the price range (+/-40 is "
"the upper and lower bound, which has no practical significance): "
"(-40,-3],(-3,-2],(-2,2],(2,3],(3,40] (the specific price is equal to "
"the mean plus a multiple of the standard deviation) [-0.5, -0.3, 0.0, "
"0.3, 0.5] (capital ratio; the negative sign here indicates opening a "
"short position, and it is set to allow holding short positions during "
"backtesting)."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_05_类网格交易.md:12
msgid ""
"回测数据为:HS300指数的1min数据 回测时间为:2022-03-01 09:30:00到"
"2022-07-31 15:00:00"
msgstr ""
"The backtesting data consists of 1-minute data points for the HS300 "
"index. The backtesting period is from 09:30:00 on March 1, 2022 to "
"15:00:00 on July 31, 2022."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_05_类网格交易.md:20
msgid "定义交易策略"
msgstr "Define trading strategy"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_05_类网格交易.md:65
msgid "设定交易员对象，并且设置交易配置，实施交易回测"
msgstr ""
"Define the trader object, configure the trading settings, and perform "
"trading backtesting."

